name: Mia Khalifa
description:
Our favorite American-Lebanese reporter and media personality, Mia Khalifa!

Honestly, this one was hell to finetune. Due to her time in the spotlight being rather short, it was surprisingly tedious to gather a workable dataset for her. Had to rerun the process up to 4 times and do a lot of testing.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. Due to limitations in the dataset, there are difficulties getting a wide variety in backgrounds and clothing. Using the Embedding at a lower weight like Koh_MiaKhalifa:0.85 or using inpainting helps a lot.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
